@node Method_D__OS_1_3__MountList_file_ "Method D: OS 1.3 (MountList file)"
@{i}Method D: OS 1.3 (MountList file)@{ui}

Edit @{fg shine}DEVS:MountList@{fg text} and append:

@{fg highlight}
  CF0:
      Device = scsi.device
      /* ... other entries ... */
@{fg text}

Then mount with:

@{fg highlight}
  mount CF0:
@{fg text}

----------------------------------------
