@node dd_Usage "dd Usage"
@{i}dd Usage@{ui}

Copy disk blocks to file:

@{fg highlight}
  dd scsi.device 1 ram:dump 0 128
@{fg text}

Write file back to disk:

@{fg highlight}
  dd ram:dump scsi.device 1 0 128
@{fg text}

----------------------------------------
@{"<< Prev" link Tools_Included}  @{"Contents" link Main}  @{"Next >>" link Debug95}

@endnode

@node Debug95 "Debug95"
@{i}Debug95@{ui}

Creates a dump of internal fat95 variables for diagnosis.
@{fg highlight}
  debug95 CF0: ram:cf0.log
@{fg text}

----------------------------------------
@{"<< Prev" link dd_Usage}  @{"Contents" link Main}  @{"Next >>" link boot95}

@endnode

@node boot95 "boot95"
@{i}boot95@{ui}

Booting from FAT Partition
@{fg highlight}
  boot95 CF0:
@{fg text}

This installs an Amiga automount sequence in the unused area between
the MBR and first partition (~30KB). Requires fat95 in @{fg shine}L:@{fg text} drawer.

@{b}Caution:@{ub} Overwrites existing Amiga style partitioning info.

----------------------------------------
@{"<< Prev" link Debug95}  @{"Contents" link Main}  @{"Next >>" link License}

@endnode

